`.github/` holds this repo's GitHub-native automation; it currently contains only the `workflows/` subdirectory. There's nothing at this level besides that one child — no shared config, issue templates, or other GitHub-specific files.

`workflows/` is a single CI/CD pipeline that deploys a static visualization site to GitHub Pages, with a fragile three-way coupling (binary name, output path, HTML fetch path) that CI does not verify.

No intent.md exists for this directory to check against.